```plantuml
@startuml boot2podman_machine

actor User

participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "Libmachine" as Libmachine
participant "Driver" as Driver
participant "Provisioner" as Provisioner
participant "Host" as Host

User -> CLI: execute `create`
CLI -> Libmachine: NewHost()
Libmachine -> Driver: Create()
Driver -> Host: Initialize VM
Host -> Provisioner: Provision VM
Provisioner -> Driver: Configure Podman
Driver -> Libmachine: Return VM Details
Libmachine -> CLI: Return Success

User -> CLI: execute `start`
CLI -> Libmachine: Load()
Libmachine -> Driver: Start()
Driver -> Host: Boot VM
Host -> Provisioner: Verify Podman
Provisioner -> Driver: Check Status
Driver -> Libmachine: Return Status
Libmachine -> CLI: Return Success

User -> CLI: execute `stop`
CLI -> Libmachine: Load()
Libmachine -> Driver: Stop()
Driver -> Host: Power Down VM
Host -> Provisioner: Ensure Shutdown
Provisioner -> Driver: Confirm Stop
Driver -> Libmachine: Return Status
Libmachine -> CLI: Return Success

User -> CLI: execute `rm`
CLI -> Libmachine: Load()
Libmachine -> Driver: Remove()
Driver -> Host: Delete VM
Driver -> Libmachine: Return Removal Status
Libmachine -> CLI: Return Success

@enduml
```